# Get Cluster health
GET _cluster/health

#Number of nodes
GET _cat/node?v

# Details about indices
GET _cat/indices?v

#Details about shards
GET _cat/shards?v

# Adding an index 
PUT pages

Notes:

1. A cluster health is yellow when index has replica but on same node
	1. Creating a new node will make the status green (ES places the replica on the new node created)
	

